<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 22:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列警方非法拘留11名反政府抗议者近一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-unlawfully-holds-11-anti-government-protesters-in-custody-for-nearly-a-day/00000190-22c3-d3e6-a191-76ebac3b0000</link><description>周日早上，警方提出了限制释放抗议者的请求，但到下午，只有三人按照法律要求被带去参加第一次保释听证会。被捕并随后被释放的人包括《国土报》摄影师伊泰·罗恩 (Itai Ron)</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 21:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-unlawfully-holds-11-anti-government-protesters-in-custody-for-nearly-a-day/00000190-22c3-d3e6-a191-76ebac3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列联盟重新提出有争议的法案，赋予政府对城市拉比任命的权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/coalition-re-introduces-contentious-bill-giving-govt-power-over-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-21d1-d880-a7f5-b5d5d7340000</link><description>由于联盟成员之间存在分歧，该法案的讨论于三月份暂停，随后将恢复讨论。该法案还允许政府任命并资助约 600 名新拉比</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/coalition-re-introduces-contentious-bill-giving-govt-power-over-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-21d1-d880-a7f5-b5d5d7340000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院规定，父亲在出生后皈依基督教的孩子可能会获得以色列公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/children-whose-fathers-converted-after-birth-may-get-israeli-citizenship-top-court-rules/00000190-2250-d3e6-a191-767bc21e0000</link><description>Ronnen 和 Vogelman 法官表示，授予身份符合《公民法》保护家庭单位和确保儿童福利的客观目的</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/children-whose-fathers-converted-after-birth-may-get-israeli-citizenship-top-court-rules/00000190-2250-d3e6-a191-767bc21e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府组织在联合新闻发布会上呼吁“抵抗周”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-anti-government-groups-call-for-week-of-resistance-in-joint-press-conference/00000190-21d5-d4b4-a7d6-e9f7ed320000</link><description>经过动荡的一周后，三个抗议团体正在为为期一周的全国性抗议和封锁做准备，呼吁所有以色列人立即加入他们的选举要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-anti-government-groups-call-for-week-of-resistance-in-joint-press-conference/00000190-21d5-d4b4-a7d6-e9f7ed320000</guid></item><item><title>定居者在西岸袭击巴勒斯坦牧羊人和以色列活动人士</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/settlers-assault-palestinian-shepherds-israeli-activists-in-west-bank/00000190-2235-df11-a3b9-a337fabe0000</link><description>活动人士称，定居者曾两次殴打他们以及他们正在帮助的牧羊人，并向他们投掷石块</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/settlers-assault-palestinian-shepherds-israeli-activists-in-west-bank/00000190-2235-df11-a3b9-a337fabe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会小组推动将预备役军人豁免年龄延长一年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-advances-move-to-extend-raising-exemption-age-for-reservists-by-a-year/00000190-2234-d880-a7f5-b6f4507b0000</link><description>规范该措施的紧急命令将于六月底到期，即生效四个月后。如果议会通过该提案，士兵将在预备役服役至41岁，军官将服役至46岁，担任关键职务的预备役人员将服役至50岁</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-advances-move-to-extend-raising-exemption-age-for-reservists-by-a-year/00000190-2234-d880-a7f5-b6f4507b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前议员在讨论加沙战争时引用希特勒的话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/former-israeli-mk-quotes-hitler-while-discussing-gaza-war/00000190-224f-d231-a1b2-e65f76fe0000</link><description>摩西·费林 (Moshe Feiglin) 对第 12 频道新闻说：“正如希特勒所说，如果只剩下一名犹太人，我就无法生存”，如果加沙还剩下一名“伊斯兰纳粹分子”，我们就无法生活在这里。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:52:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/former-israeli-mk-quotes-hitler-while-discussing-gaza-war/00000190-224f-d231-a1b2-e65f76fe0000</guid></item><item><title>一名新的民警正在记录以色列反政府抗议活动中警察的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-new-civilian-guard-is-documenting-police-brutality-at-israels-anti-government-protests/00000190-2134-d880-a7f5-b5f4d8f40000</link><description>Magen Ezrachi（又称“平民盾牌”）让志愿者到现场记录抗议活动中的虐待行为，在本-格维尔的统治下，以色列警察一直对示威者、记者甚至在加沙被扣押的人质家人使用武力。一名志愿者说：“我不应该害怕保护我的执法组织”</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:47:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-new-civilian-guard-is-documenting-police-brutality-at-israels-anti-government-protests/00000190-2134-d880-a7f5-b5f4d8f40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对遵守犹太安息日的愤世嫉俗的规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-16/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-cynical-rules-for-observing-the-jewish-sabbath/00000190-21dd-dee3-af9b-e7dd60010000</link><description>以色列总理通常不会在周六犹太安息日期间发布公开信息。自加沙战争爆发以来，内塔尼亚胡已经两次打破了它，这完美地解释了他无与伦比的政治犬儒主义</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 17:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-16/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-cynical-rules-for-observing-the-jewish-sabbath/00000190-21dd-dee3-af9b-e7dd60010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 254 天：以色列国防军否认内塔尼亚胡不知道拉法暂停的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-254-idf-rejects-claim-netanyahu-didnt-know-about-pauses-in-rafah/00000190-21ef-df11-a3b9-a1ef364a0000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布每天在拉法进行“战术暂停”，以便向加沙提供更多援助 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特声称他们不知道这一决定 ■ 以色列最高法院于 10 月 7 日下令停止国家审计长对国防机构失败的调查 ■ 哈马斯政治局局长哈尼亚表示，该组织对当前停战提案的回应符合拜登提出的原则 ■ 这是战争开始 254 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 16:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-254-idf-rejects-claim-netanyahu-didnt-know-about-pauses-in-rafah/00000190-21ef-df11-a3b9-a1ef364a0000</guid></item><item><title>和平企业家毛兹·伊农 (Maoz Inon) 在拿撒勒这座“希望悬崖上的城市”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-nazareth-city-on-the-precipice-of-hope-with-peace-entrepreneur-maoz-inon/00000190-20a8-d3e6-a191-76abb5d40000</link><description>2020 年，随着 COVID-19 大流行的肆虐，伊农开始了他的拿撒勒之旅。现在，10 月 7 日他的父母在以色列南部被哈马斯杀害后，他向参与者讲述了“创造希望”的行为以及旅游业作为共存力量的故事</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 13:49:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-nazareth-city-on-the-precipice-of-hope-with-peace-entrepreneur-maoz-inon/00000190-20a8-d3e6-a191-76abb5d40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院叫停国家审计长对以色列国防军辛贝特 10 月 7 日失败的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-halts-state-comptrollers-probe-into-idf-shin-bet-oct-7-failures/00000190-2103-d3e6-a191-772b73890000</link><description>吉拉·坎菲·斯坦尼茨法官以“复杂的安全局势”为由解释了法院的决定，并补充说，推迟调查的决定也是根据国防官员向法院提交的机密声明而做出的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 13:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-halts-state-comptrollers-probe-into-idf-shin-bet-oct-7-failures/00000190-2103-d3e6-a191-772b73890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布每日“战术暂停”加沙战斗，以允许援助物资进入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-daily-tactical-pause-in-gaza-fighting-to-allow-for-entry-of-aid/00000190-20cb-df6a-a3f6-2fdbe7120000</link><description>尽管内塔尼亚胡总理办公室否认总理了解这一政策，但军方官员表示，这符合他的命令。与国防部长加兰特关系密切的消息人士称，他并不了解军队的决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-daily-tactical-pause-in-gaza-fighting-to-allow-for-entry-of-aid/00000190-20cb-df6a-a3f6-2fdbe7120000</guid></item><item><title>“课堂内外的以色列和巴勒斯坦话语有多么不同，令人震惊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-16/ty-article-podcast/its-striking-how-different-israel-palestine-discourse-is-in-the-classroom-and-out-of-it/00000190-1204-d667-abf0-76cf342b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 12:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-16/ty-article-podcast/its-striking-how-different-israel-palestine-discourse-is-in-the-classroom-and-out-of-it/00000190-1204-d667-abf0-76cf342b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人对哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的支持表明了他们与以色列人的共同点：绝望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-support-for-hamas-oct-7-attack-shows-what-they-share-with-israelis-despair/00000190-2075-d880-a7f5-b4f58bcf0000</link><description>一项针对加沙和西岸巴勒斯坦人的最新民意调查显示，八个月的流血和破坏并没有削弱人们对哈马斯及其 10 月 7 日袭击的支持。对于以色列人、巴勒斯坦人和国际社会来说，其结果表明为什么冲突的新解决方案如此迫切</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-support-for-hamas-oct-7-attack-shows-what-they-share-with-israelis-despair/00000190-2075-d880-a7f5-b4f58bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学特别工作组揭露了自 10 月 7 日以来校园内学生和教职人员普遍存在的反犹太主义行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-task-force-reveals-full-extent-of-antisemitism-on-campus-since-oct-7/00000190-205f-d880-a7f5-b4df117d0000</link><description>教授的反犹太主义言论、对犹太学生的骚扰——哥伦比亚大学反犹太主义特别工作组自 11 月成立以来已听取了数百份证词。其成员向《国土报》讲述了他们计划的强制方向，并表示他们已经就反犹太主义的“教育”定义达成一致。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 11:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/columbia-task-force-reveals-full-extent-of-antisemitism-on-campus-since-oct-7/00000190-205f-d880-a7f5-b4df117d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻自由遭到破坏的历史性一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/a-historic-day-in-the-destruction-of-israels-free-press/00000190-2067-df11-a3b9-a1671a220000</link><description>亿万富翁 Len Blavatnik 决定任命 Yulia Shamalov-Berkovich 为第 13 频道新闻首席执行官，标志着该频道作为强硬新闻机构的精神的终结。内塔尼亚胡还有另一个微笑的理由</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 10:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/a-historic-day-in-the-destruction-of-israels-free-press/00000190-2067-df11-a3b9-a1671a220000</guid></item><item><title>法国军火博览会组织者对禁止以色列国民参加活动的裁决提出上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/french-arms-expo-organizers-appeal-ruling-banning-israeli-nationals-from-event/00000190-2024-d3e6-a191-762f1ef40000</link><description>组织者表示，法院的裁决曲解了他们的意图，全面禁止以色列参加展览。消息人士称，这一决定遭到了以色列国防部长的严厉回应，法国国防部认为这一决定是不可接受的</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 09:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/french-arms-expo-organizers-appeal-ruling-banning-israeli-nationals-from-event/00000190-2024-d3e6-a191-762f1ef40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在周六拉法爆炸中丧生的七名士兵的名字，其中三名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-five-soldiers-killed-in-saturdays-rafah-blast-and-two-killed-in-northern-gaza/00000190-1fd3-d4b4-a7d6-dff30cc60000</link><description>周日，军方还公布了一名在战斗中丧生的士兵的名字，一天前，八名士兵在装甲运兵车爆炸中丧生。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 08:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-five-soldiers-killed-in-saturdays-rafah-blast-and-two-killed-in-northern-gaza/00000190-1fd3-d4b4-a7d6-dff30cc60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和以色列国防军高层就加沙停火展开斗争，同时与真主党展开全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-top-brass-fight-over-gaza-truce-while-spiraling-towards-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-1d17-d231-a1b2-fd5fbd450000</link><description>周六八名以色列国防军士兵的死亡表明，面对哈马斯的适应性策略是困难的，哈马斯将其转变为松散的游击队组织 ■ 内塔尼亚胡继续推销“全面胜利”，再次委托其他人传递坏消息</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-top-brass-fight-over-gaza-truce-while-spiraling-towards-war-with-hezbollah/00000190-1d17-d231-a1b2-fd5fbd450000</guid></item></channel></rss>